title: Crtsh
description: This connector integrates Cert.SH data with the OpenCTI platform, facilitating automated import and management of cybersecurity information. It allows users to track relevant intelligence and threats by importing domain-related data from Cert.SH into OpenCTI.
short_description: This connector integrates Cert.SH data with the OpenCTI platform, facilitating automated import and management of cybersecurity information. It allows users to track relevant intelligence and threats by importing domain-related data from Cert.SH into OpenCTI.
